name: CSC DOMAIN MANAGER [Zone Edit Requested]
description: CSC received a request through Domain Manager to change DNS zone records on a vital domain using CSC's name servers.

name: CSC DOMAIN MANAGER [DNS Change Requested]
description: CSC received a request through Domain Manager to change DNS on a vital domain.

name: CSC DOMAIN MANAGER [Multilock Removed Requested]
description: CSC received a request through Domain Manager to remove MultiLock (registry locks) from a vital domain.

name: CSC DOMAIN MANAGER [Lapse Requested]
description: CSC received a request through Domain Manager to lapse a vital domain.

name: CSC DOMAIN MANAGER [Transfer Out Requested]
description: CSC received a request through Domain Manager to transfer out a vital domain.

name: CSC DOMAIN MANAGER [Vital Domain Added]
description: A domain has been marked as "Vital" by a user.

name: CSC DOMAIN MANAGER [WHOIS Contact Change Requested]
description: CSC received a request through Domain Manager to change WHOIS contacts on a vital domain.

name: CSC DOMAIN MANAGER [New User Added]
description: A new user has been added to the clients account.

name: CSC DOMAIN MANAGER [User Permission Added]
description: An existing user in the client's account has received a new "high-risk" role.

name: CSC DOMAIN MANAGER [Login]
description: A user has logged in to CSC Domain Manager.
